a dish I make on repeat in the summer months. When I tell you that I sometimes make three or four times a week, that is not an exaggeration. The tangy dressing paired with the crunch of the nuts and the creamy cheese – it’s perfect.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-98682\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chilled asparagus crunch salad\" width=\"1627\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/asparagus-crunch-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chilled Asparagus Crunch Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-scaled.jpg 1627w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-728x985.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-768x1039.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-1136x1536.jpg 1136w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-1514x2048.jpg 1514w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-150x203.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1627px) 100vw, 1627px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201627%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-scaled.jpg 1627w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-728x985.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-768x1039.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-1136x1536.jpg 1136w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-1514x2048.jpg 1514w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-150x203.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSo I’ve been making the same thing with asparagus too! The asparagus gets blanched just like the green beans. Then it’s covered with everything:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe blue cheese\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe toasted walnuts\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd the lemony dressing\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI find that this recipe is such a hit with the asparagus because it is full of vibrance and crunchy bites. The general flavors here are pretty “normal” – as my family would say. Ha! Okay, minus the blue cheese. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chilled asparagus crunch salad\" width=\"1728\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/asparagus-crunch-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chilled Asparagus Crunch Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-scaled.jpg 1728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-728x927.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-1609x2048.jpg 1609w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1728px) 100vw, 1728px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201728%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-scaled.jpg 1728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-728x927.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-768x978.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-1609x2048.jpg 1609w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-150x191.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWe don’t have anything too wild going on, nothing spicy, nothing overly sour or even too crunchy. If you’re flipped out over the blue cheese, use feta instead. Or even parmesan. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBasically, everything is perfect and pleasurable to the palate! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chilled asparagus crunch salad\" width=\"1729\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/asparagus-crunch-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chilled Asparagus Crunch Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-scaled.jpg 1729w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-728x926.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-768x977.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-1610x2048.jpg 1610w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1729px) 100vw, 1729px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201729%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-scaled.jpg 1729w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-728x926.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-768x977.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-1207x1536.jpg 1207w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-1610x2048.jpg 1610w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-150x191.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe other thing I love about this recipe is that you can really make the asparagus any way you’d like. I find it is much more forgiving than the green beans. You can blanch it, but you can also roast it. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd you can even \u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2021/03/grilled-asparagus-caesar-salad/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003egrill\u003c/a\u003e it too, which is probably my #1 way to make asparagus. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chilled asparagus crunch salad\" width=\"1772\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/asparagus-crunch-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chilled Asparagus Crunch Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-scaled.jpg 1772w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-728x904.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-768x953.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-1238x1536.jpg 1238w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-1650x2048.jpg 1650w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-150x186.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1772px) 100vw, 1772px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201772%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-scaled.jpg 1772w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-728x904.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-768x953.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-1238x1536.jpg 1238w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-1650x2048.jpg 1650w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-150x186.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSo there you go. An embarrassingly easy dish, but one that is super satisfying this time of year!! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chilled asparagus crunch salad\" width=\"1739\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/asparagus-crunch-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chilled Asparagus Crunch Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-scaled.jpg 1739w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-728x921.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-768x972.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-1214x1536.jpg 1214w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-1619x2048.jpg 1619w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-150x190.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1739px) 100vw, 1739px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201739%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-scaled.jpg 1739w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-728x921.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-768x972.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-1214x1536.jpg 1214w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-1619x2048.jpg 1619w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-150x190.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-10-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eAsparagus Crunch Salad\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-98694\" data-recipe-id=\"98694\" data-servings=\"2\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-5-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSpring Asparagus Crunch Salad\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"98694\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis cold asparagus crunch salad is filled with so much flavor and texture, including toasted walnuts, creamy blue cheese and a tangy dijon dressing. It\u0026#39;s a fantastic spring side dish!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98694\" data-servings=\"2\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epound\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efresh asparagus spears,,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ewoody ends trimmed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e⅓\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etoasted walnuts,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e⅓\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecrumbled blue cheese\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"98694\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98694-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eStart by blanching the asparagus . Prepare an ice bath - fill a large bowl with ice and cold water.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98694-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBring a large pot of water to a boil. Once boiling, add the asparagus and cook for 3 to 4 minutes (add an additional minute or 2 if the spears are thick!). Use a strainer to immediately transfer the spears to the ice bath. Let them chill in the bath for 5 minutes. Pat them dry with a paper towel.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98694-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the asparagus on the plate and give it a light sprinkle of salt and pepper. Drizzle on the dijon dressing. Top with the crumbled blue cheese and walnuts. Serve immediately. This tastes incredible cold - like leftovers right out of the fridge. It’s also great at room temperature!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003elemony dijon dressing\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-98694-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a bowl, whisk together the lemon juice and mustard. Whisk in the oil until the dressing is emulsified. Add a pinch of salt and pepper along with the herbs. Whisk to combine. Any extras of this stays great in the fridge for a few days - it just has to be whisked and stirred before using!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSalad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"chilled asparagus crunch salad\" width=\"1753\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/04/asparagus-crunch-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Chilled Asparagus Crunch Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-scaled.jpg 1753w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-728x914.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-768x964.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-1224x1536.jpg 1224w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-1632x2048.jpg 1632w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aspragus-crunch-salad-9-150x188.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1753px) 100vw, 1753px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%